---
title: "Omaha Fish Fry Tracker"
permalink: /fishfry/index.html
description: "16+ years of Omaha-area Lenten fish fry adventures, tracked since 2010"
layout: base
---

<article class="region page">
  <div class="wrapper flow prose">
    <h1 class="page-title">🐟 Omaha Fish Fry Tracker</h1>
    <p>
      What started as fun family outings in 2010 has become a {{ fishfryStats.seasonCount }}-year tradition
      to enjoy the best Frydays in the Omaha metro. Every Friday during Lent, we're out there
      eating 🐟 & 🍤, sampling 🍻🍹, and winning meat wheels along the way
    </p>

    <h2>📊 By the Numbers</h2>
    <div class="fishfry-stats-grid">
      <div class="fishfry-stat">
        <span class="fishfry-stat-number">{{ fishfryStats.localVisits }}</span>
        <span class="fishfry-stat-label">Total Fish Frys</span>
      </div>
      <div class="fishfry-stat">
        <span class="fishfry-stat-number">{{ fishfryStats.seasonCount }}</span>
        <span class="fishfry-stat-label">Seasons</span>
      </div>
      <div class="fishfry-stat">
        <span class="fishfry-stat-number">{{ fishfryStats.uniqueVenues }}</span>
        <span class="fishfry-stat-label">Unique Venues</span>
      </div>
      <div class="fishfry-stat">
        <span class="fishfry-stat-number">{{ fishfryStats.bestYear.year }}</span>
        <span class="fishfry-stat-label">Best Season ({{ fishfryStats.bestYear.count }})</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fishfry-rankings">
      <div class="fishfry-rankings-col">
        <h2>🏆 Hall of Fame</h2>
        <p>Most-visited fish frys across all seasons:</p>
        <table class="fishfry-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Rank</th>
              <th>Venue</th>
              <th>Visits</th>
              <th>Seasons</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {% for venue in fishfryStats.hallOfFame %}
              <tr>
                <td>{{ loop.index }}</td>
                <td>{{ venue.name }}</td>
                <td>{{ venue.count }}</td>
                <td><small>{{ venue.years }}</small></td>
              </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="fishfry-rankings-col">
        <h2>🔥 Fresh Fryers</h2>
        <p>The reel regulars, last 4 seasons:</p>
        <table class="fishfry-table fishfry-table--compact">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Venue</th>
              <th>Recent Visits</th>
              <th>Seasons</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {% for venue in fishfryStats.freshFryers %}
              <tr>
                <td>{{ venue.name }}</td>
                <td>{{ venue.count }}</td>
                <td><small>{{ venue.recentYears }}</small></td>
              </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="fishfry-streak">🔥 <strong>Holy Ghost</strong> is on a <strong>{{ fishfryStats.holyGhostStreak }}-season streak</strong> &mdash; every (possible) year since {{ fishfryStats.holyGhostStreakStart }}!</p>

    <h3>🎸 One-Hit Wonders</h3>
    <p class="fishfry-one-hits">
      {% for venue in fishfryStats.oneHitWonders %}{{ venue.name }} <small>({{ venue.years }})</small>{{ ", " if not loop.last }}{% endfor %}
    </p>

    <h2>📅 Season by Season</h2>

    <div class="fishfry-grid">
    {% for season in fishfry.seasons | reverse %}
      <div class="fishfry-card {{ 'fishfry-card--current' if loop.first }}" id="season-{{ season.year }}">
        <h3>
          <a href="#season-{{ season.year }}" class="heading-anchor">{{ season.year }}</a>
          {% if loop.first %}<span class="fishfry-current-badge">Current Season</span>{% endif %}
          {% set localCount = fishfryStats.seasonLocalCounts[season.year] %}
          {% if localCount > 0 %}
            <span class="fishfry-season-count"><span class="fishfry-season-number">{{ localCount }}</span> fish fry{{ "s" if localCount != 1 }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        </h3>
        {% if season.visits | length > 0 %}
          <ul class="fishfry-visit-list">
            {% for visit in season.visits %}
              <li class="fishfry-visit {{ 'fishfry-visit--away' if visit.away }}">
                <span class="fishfry-visit-top">{{ "✈️" if visit.away else "🐟" }}
                  <span class="fishfry-visit-name">{{ visit.name }}</span>
                  {%- if visit.location %}<span class="fishfry-visit-location"> &ndash; {{ visit.location }}</span>{%- endif %}</span>
                {%- if visit.note %}<span class="fishfry-visit-note">({{ visit.note }})</span>{%- endif %}
              </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        {% endif %}
        {% if season.note %}
          <p class="fishfry-season-note">
            {% if season.note == "Coronavirus" or season.note == "Covid-19" %}
              {{ season.note }} 😞
            {% elif season.note == "Unknown" %}
              🤷 Lost to history
            {% else %}
              {{ season.note }}
            {% endif %}
          </p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</article>
